Place SDF font files here:
  hell_verdict.png   — grayscale SDF atlas (R channel = distance)
  hell_verdict.json  — glyph metrics (msdf-atlas-gen format)

Generate with:
  msdf-atlas-gen -font your_font.ttf -type sdf -format png \
    -imageout hell_verdict.png -json hell_verdict.json \
    -size 48 -pxrange 4

Or use any Hiero-compatible JSON + PNG atlas.
The renderer falls back to a built-in ASCII grid if these are missing.
